text: The iPhone 3GS is a smartphone made by Apple Inc. It is the third generation iPhone, coming after iPhone 3G. It was introduced on June 8, 2009, It was released on June 19, 2009. This iPhone is named "3GS". The "S" in "iPhone 3GS" means "Speed". The iPhone 3GS has better performance, allowing it to run faster and more efficiently. It also has a higher quality camera that can take photos with higher resolution, as well as take videos with better quality. It also adds the ability to use voice control, a function where users can talk into the phone to command actions on the phone. The iPhone 3GS can also support faster downloading. It was released in the United States, Canada, and six European countries on June 19, 2009, in Australia and Japan on June 26, and worldwide in July and August 2009. ==References== ==Other websites== 3GS Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2009
